  ('西溪国家湿地公园', 7, 'Xixi Wetland Ecological Science Popularization Hall', '西溪湿地生态科普馆', '', 'https://edwvrriuwzaaqznklrgi.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/cover-images/sub-areas/all/hangzhou_xixi_wetland_sa_08.png'),
